Description:
  This generator creates the necessary files for work that extends
  Bibliocat's BiblioWork.

Example:
  rails generate bibliocat:work BibCollection

  This will create:
    app/repository_models/bib_collection.rb
    app/actors/curation_concern/bib_collection_actor.rb
    app/controllers/curation_concern/bib_collections_controller.rb
    app/views/curation_concern/bib_collections/.keep
    spec/factories/bib_collection_factory.rb
    spec/repository_models/bib_collection_spec.rb
    spec/actors/curation_concern/bib_collection_actor_spec.rb
    spec/controllers/curation_concern/bib_collections_controller_spec.rb

  This will also:
    register BibCollection as a valid curation concern in
      config/initializers/worthwhile_config.rb
